# =============================================================================
# TradeOps — VENDOR API KEYS (paste-ready)
# Primary AI: COHERE_API_KEY (server-only). Optional: OpenAI/xAI/etc.
# Paste your secret RIGHT AFTER the = sign. Leave blank if unused.
# Example:  COHERE_API_KEY=your-rotated-key
# Then copy lines into root .env  (or merge this whole file).
# Restart: pnpm stop && pnpm start
# Never commit real secrets. Compromised/chat-pasted keys: rotate, do not reuse.
# Regenerate: pnpm run env:write-key-docs
# Canonical manifest: packages/config/src/environment-manifest.ts
# =============================================================================

